{"lemma":"ضَرَّةٍ","slug":"ضَرَّةٍ","root":"ض.ر.ر","root_slug":"ض-ر-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ض-ر-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n25658","n25667","n25668"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B6%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"co-wife (by tradition not the word-choice preferred by Muslims because of the negative connotation of the root)"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Proto-Semitic *ṣ́arrat- (“co-wife”). Cognate with Akkadian 𒁮𒋰𒁀 (ṣerretum) and Biblical Hebrew צָרָה (ṣɔrɔ)."},"ipa":["/dˤar.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25658","headword_ar":"ضَرَّهُ","root":"Dr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dar~a bihi","text_ar":"ضَرَّ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dar~N","text_ar":"ضَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Msb, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DAr~hu","text_ar":"ضارّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [which see also below,] (S, A, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muDaAr~apN","text_ar":"مُضَارَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DiraArN","text_ar":"ضِرَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A, Msb, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ADr~hu","text_ar":"اضرّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi","text_ar":"بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ADr~","text_ar":"اضرّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) or both, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iDoraArN","text_ar":"اـِضْرَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, harmed, injured, hurt, marred, mischiefed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"damaged, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafaEahu","text_ar":"نَفَعَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, A, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"did to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, an act that was evil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disliked,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hated."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dar~ahu A_ilayohi","text_ar":"ضَرَّهُ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 8. ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yaDur~aka Ealayohi jamalN","text_ar":"لَا يَضُرَّكَ عَلَيْهِ جَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"No camel will be more sufficient for thee than he;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yaziyduka","text_ar":"لَا يَزِيدُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yaDur~uka Ealayohi rajulN","text_ar":"لَا يَضُرُّكَ عَلَيْهِ رَجُلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"No man will be more sufficient for thee than he;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thou wilt not find a man who will be more sufficient for thee than he;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tajidu rajulFA yaziyduka EalaY maA Einoda h`*aA","text_ar":"لَا تَجِدُ رَجُلًا يَزِيدُكَ عَلَى مَا عِنْدَ هٰذَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~ajuli mina AlkifaAyapi","text_ar":"الرَّجُلِ مِنَ الكِفَايَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (ISk, S:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA yaDur~uka EalaY","text_ar":"مَا يَضُرُّكَ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlD~ab~i SayodN","text_ar":"الضَّبِّ صَيْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"No animal that is hunted is more sufficient for thee than the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dab~","text_ar":"ضَبّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA yaDiyruka","text_ar":"مَا يَضِيرُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA taDur~uka EalayohaA jaAriyapN","text_ar":"مَا تَضُرُّكَ عَلَيْهَا جَارِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"No girl,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young woman, is more sufficient for thee than she;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA taziyduka","text_ar":"مَا تَزِيدُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA yaDur~uka Ealayohi $ayoy^FA","text_ar":"مَا يَضُرُّكَ عَلَيْهِ شَيْيًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, is not at all more sufficient for thee than he,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA yaziyduka","text_ar":"مَا يَزِيدُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IAar, TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dar~a","text_ar":"ضَرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [sec. pers. app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Darurota","text_ar":"ضَرُرْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaDur~u","text_ar":"يَضُرُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraArapN","text_ar":"ضَرَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, blind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"part. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DariyrN","text_ar":"ضَرِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (MA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Msb","K","ISk"]},{"entry_id":"n25667","headword_ar":"ضَرَّةٌ","root":"Dr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Necessity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"need;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] a subst. from 8: (K, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hardness, distressfulness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"afflictiveness, of state"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"annoyance, molestation, harm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hurt."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sgh, K.) See also ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dur~N","text_ar":"ضُرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DararN","text_ar":"ضَرَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dar~aA='u","text_ar":"ضَرَّا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaruwrapN","text_ar":"ضَرُورَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  A woman's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"husband's wife;"},{"kind":"text","text":"her"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fellow-wife:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K:) an appellation disliked by the Muslim;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaArapN","text_ar":"جَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being used in preference to it; accord. to a trad.: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraAy^iru","text_ar":"ضَرَايِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dar~aAtN","text_ar":"ضَرَّاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) the former extr. [with respect to rule]; (TA;) the latter regular. (Msb.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eal~apN","text_ar":"عَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  Hence, sing. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraAy^iru","text_ar":"ضَرَايِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Discordant things"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affairs;"},{"kind":"text","text":"likened to fellow-wives, who will not agree. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And [hence also, app.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlD~ar~ataAni","text_ar":"الضَّرَّتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a term applied to (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The two stones of a mill."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M.)       -A3-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flesh of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaroE","text_ar":"ضَرْع"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"udder"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"udder"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DrE","text_ar":"ضرع"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"altogether,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"except the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTobaA='","text_ar":"اَطْبَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"teats"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when containing milk,"},{"kind":"text","text":"but not otherwise: (TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"base of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DrE","text_ar":"ضرع"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is never,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scarcely ever, without milk in it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"base of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vadoY","text_ar":"ثَدْى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"breast"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofN","text_ar":"خِلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (K.) One says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dar~apN $akoraY","text_ar":"ضَرَّةٌ شَكْرَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A full"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dr~p","text_ar":"ضرّة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S in this art.:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dr~p","text_ar":"ضرّة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having much milk."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$kr","text_ar":"شكر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dar~apu AlA_ibohaAmi","text_ar":"ضَرَّةُ الاـِبْهَامِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The portion of flesh that is beneath the thumb, which is what corresponds to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloyah","text_ar":"اَلْيَه"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the hand:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlD~ar~apu","text_ar":"الضَّرَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the portion of the palm of the hand extending from beneath the little finger to the wrist:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, in his “ Khalk el-Insán: ”) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the inner side of the hand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"over against the little finger, corresponding to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alyp","text_ar":"الية"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the hand:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the portion of flesh beneath the thumb:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the root thereof"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. of the thumb]: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that part of the flesh of the sole of the foot upon which one treads, next the great toe."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloyapN","text_ar":"اَلْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-  The pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dar~apN","text_ar":"ضَرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(in all the senses expl. above, TA) is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraAy^iru","text_ar":"ضَرَايِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) which [as said above] is extr. (TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlD~ar~ataAni","text_ar":"الضَّرَّتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The buttocks, on each side of the bone thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the two flabby portions of flesh, on each side."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.)       -A4-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Much property,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"many cattle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exclusive of money:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"property,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cattle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mAl","text_ar":"مال"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon which one relies"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for his maintenance"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but belonging to another,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"others,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of his relations:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a detached number of cattle, of camels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","S","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n25668","headword_ar":"ضُرَّةٌ","root":"Dr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dar~aA='u","text_ar":"ضَرَّا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}